    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir in your <strong>dried basil</strong> and <strong>dried oregano</strong> – this is your <strong>herby stock</strong></p><p>Slice <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> into rounds and set them aside for later</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
