        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 35 min, remove the dish[es] from the oven and pour the <strong>herby stock</strong> all over the potatoes and tomatoes</p><p>Top with your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong></p><p>Squeeze over the juice of the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> and top the basa with the<strong> reserved lemon slices</strong></p>",
